---
interface Props {
  context?: "article" | "architecture";
  lang?: "fr" | "en";
}

const { context = "article", lang = "fr" } = Astro.props;

const copy = {
  fr: {
    ariaLabel:
      "Schéma : le téléphone envoie la requête WebDAV vers Cloudflare, qui la relaie au serveur via un tunnel sortant initié par le serveur ; à l'intérieur, le proxy interne relaie vers le serveur WebDAV (mod_dav), qui écrit dans le coffre-fort chiffré. Le correctif — réécriture de l'en-tête Destination de https:// vers http:// — se situe juste avant le serveur WebDAV, là où le schéma public et le schéma interne cessaient de correspondre.",
    telephone: "téléphone",
    telephoneSub: "client WebDAV",
    cloudflare: "Cloudflare",
    cloudflareSub: "TLS, edge public",
    serveurAws: "serveur AWS",
    tunnelSortant: "tunnel sortant",
    proxyInterne: "proxy interne",
    proxyInterneSub: "http:// interne",
    serveurWebdav: "serveur WebDAV",
    serveurWebdavSub: "mod_dav",
    coffreFort: "coffre-fort",
    coffreFortSub: ".kdbx chiffré",
    correctifIci: "correctif ici",
    correctifLine1: "Destination :",
    correctifLine2: "https:// → http://",
  },
  en: {
    ariaLabel:
      "Diagram: the phone sends the WebDAV request to Cloudflare, which relays it to the server through an outbound tunnel initiated by the server; inside, the internal proxy relays to the WebDAV server (mod_dav), which writes to the encrypted vault. The fix — rewriting the Destination header from https:// to http:// — sits right before the WebDAV server, where the public and internal schemes stopped matching.",
    telephone: "phone",
    telephoneSub: "WebDAV client",
    cloudflare: "Cloudflare",
    cloudflareSub: "TLS, public edge",
    serveurAws: "AWS server",
    tunnelSortant: "outbound tunnel",
    proxyInterne: "internal proxy",
    proxyInterneSub: "internal http://",
    serveurWebdav: "WebDAV server",
    serveurWebdavSub: "mod_dav",
    coffreFort: "vault",
    coffreFortSub: "encrypted .kdbx",
    correctifIci: "fix goes here",
    correctifLine1: "Destination:",
    correctifLine2: "https:// → http://",
  },
} as const;

const t = copy[lang];
---

<figure class="webdav-diagram">
  <div class="diagram-wrap">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 900 300" role="img" aria-label={t.ariaLabel}>
      <defs>
        <marker id="wd-arrow" viewBox="0 0 10 10" refX="9" refY="5" markerWidth="7" markerHeight="7" orient="auto-start-reverse">
          <path d="M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 z" fill="var(--text-faint)" />
        </marker>
        <marker id="wd-arrow-live" viewBox="0 0 10 10" refX="9" refY="5" markerWidth="7" markerHeight="7" orient="auto-start-reverse">
          <path d="M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 z" fill="var(--accent-live)" />
        </marker>
      </defs>

      <!-- téléphone -->
      <rect x="20" y="115" width="130" height="60" rx="6" fill="var(--panel)" stroke="var(--panel-border)" stroke-width="1.5" />
      <text x="85" y="140" text-anchor="middle" font-family="var(--font-display)" font-size="12" font-weight="600" fill="var(--text)">{t.telephone}</text>
      <text x="85" y="157" text-anchor="middle" font-family="var(--font-mono)" font-size="10.5" fill="var(--text-faint)">{t.telephoneSub}</text>

      <!-- Cloudflare -->
      <rect x="200" y="115" width="140" height="60" rx="6" fill="var(--panel)" stroke="var(--panel-border)" stroke-width="1.5" />
      <text x="270" y="140" text-anchor="middle" font-family="var(--font-display)" font-size="12" font-weight="600" fill="var(--text)">{t.cloudflare}</text>
      <text x="270" y="157" text-anchor="middle" font-family="var(--font-mono)" font-size="10.5" fill="var(--text-faint)">{t.cloudflareSub}</text>

      <path d="M150,145 L198,145" fill="none" stroke="var(--text-faint)" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#wd-arrow)" />

      <!-- Serveur AWS -->
      <rect x="390" y="70" width="480" height="210" rx="8" fill="none" stroke="var(--panel-border)" stroke-width="1.5" />
      <text x="408" y="90" font-family="var(--font-display)" font-size="12" font-weight="600" fill="var(--text)">{t.serveurAws}</text>

      <path d="M340,145 L388,145" fill="none" stroke="var(--text-faint)" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#wd-arrow)" />
      <path d="M388,178 L340,178" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent-live)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="5 4" marker-end="url(#wd-arrow-live)" />
      <text x="364" y="197" text-anchor="middle" font-family="var(--font-mono)" font-size="10" fill="var(--accent-live)">{t.tunnelSortant}</text>

      <!-- proxy interne -->
      <rect x="410" y="100" width="150" height="55" rx="4" fill="var(--panel)" stroke="var(--panel-border)" />
      <text x="485" y="121" text-anchor="middle" font-family="var(--font-mono)" font-size="12" fill="var(--text)">{t.proxyInterne}</text>
      <text x="485" y="138" text-anchor="middle" font-family="var(--font-mono)" font-size="10" fill="var(--text-faint)">{t.proxyInterneSub}</text>

      <!-- serveur WebDAV -->
      <rect x="620" y="100" width="150" height="55" rx="4" fill="var(--panel)" stroke="var(--panel-border)" />
      <text x="695" y="121" text-anchor="middle" font-family="var(--font-mono)" font-size="12" fill="var(--text)">{t.serveurWebdav}</text>
      <text x="695" y="138" text-anchor="middle" font-family="var(--font-mono)" font-size="10" fill="var(--text-faint)">{t.serveurWebdavSub}</text>

      <path d="M560,127 L618,127" fill="none" stroke="var(--text-faint)" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#wd-arrow)" />

      <!-- coffre-fort -->
      <rect x="620" y="195" width="150" height="55" rx="4" fill="var(--panel)" stroke="var(--panel-border)" />
      <text x="695" y="216" text-anchor="middle" font-family="var(--font-mono)" font-size="12" fill="var(--text)">{t.coffreFort}</text>
      <text x="695" y="233" text-anchor="middle" font-family="var(--font-mono)" font-size="10" fill="var(--text-faint)">{t.coffreFortSub}</text>

      <path d="M695,155 L695,193" fill="none" stroke="var(--text-faint)" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#wd-arrow)" />

      <!-- correctif : réécriture de l'en-tête Destination -->
      <rect x="410" y="195" width="150" height="55" rx="4" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent-live)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="4 3" />
      <text x="485" y="213" text-anchor="middle" font-family="var(--font-mono)" font-size="11" font-weight="600" fill="var(--accent-live)">{t.correctifIci}</text>
      <text x="485" y="228" text-anchor="middle" font-family="var(--font-mono)" font-size="9.5" fill="var(--accent-live)">{t.correctifLine1}</text>
      <text x="485" y="240" text-anchor="middle" font-family="var(--font-mono)" font-size="9.5" fill="var(--accent-live)">{t.correctifLine2}</text>
      <path d="M485,193 L485,158" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent-live)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="3 3" />
    </svg>
  </div>
  <figcaption>
    {
      context === "architecture" ? (
        lang === "en" ? (
          <>
            Detail of the <a href="/inventaire/proxy-inverse/">reverse proxy</a> role: WebDAV's{" "}
            <code>MOVE</code>/<code>COPY</code> commands carry an absolute URL in the <code>Destination</code>{" "}
            header, built by the client with the public scheme (<code>https://</code>) — but the WebDAV module,
            behind the proxy, only speaks <code>http://</code> internally. The fix rewrites that header right
            before it reaches the module. See the article:{" "}
            <a href="/blog/le-move-qui-echouait-une-histoire-de-proxy-de-schema-http-et-dun-coffre-fort-presque-corrompu/">
              the MOVE that kept failing
            </a>.
          </>
        ) : (
          <>
            Détail du rôle <a href="/inventaire/proxy-inverse/">proxy inverse</a> : les commandes WebDAV{" "}
            <code>MOVE</code>/<code>COPY</code> transportent une URL absolue dans l'en-tête <code>Destination</code>,
            construite par le client avec le schéma public (<code>https://</code>) — mais le module WebDAV, derrière
            le proxy, ne parle que <code>http://</code> en interne. Le correctif réécrit cet en-tête juste avant qu'il
            n'atteigne le module. Voir l'article :{" "}
            <a href="/blog/le-move-qui-echouait-une-histoire-de-proxy-de-schema-http-et-dun-coffre-fort-presque-corrompu/">
              le MOVE qui échouait
            </a>.
          </>
        )
      ) : lang === "en" ? (
        <>
          The path of a <code>MOVE</code> request: from the phone to the encrypted vault, through the point where
          the <code>Destination</code> header must be rewritten for the scheme to match. See the{" "}
          <a href="/architecture/">architecture overview</a>.
        </>
      ) : (
        <>
          Le chemin d'une requête <code>MOVE</code> : du téléphone au coffre-fort chiffré, en passant par le point
          où l'en-tête <code>Destination</code> doit être réécrit pour que le schéma corresponde. Voir la{" "}
          <a href="/architecture/">vue d'ensemble de l'architecture</a>.
        </>
      )
    }
  </figcaption>
</figure>

<style>
  .webdav-diagram {
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }

  .diagram-wrap {
    overflow-x: auto;
    border: 1px solid var(--panel-border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: var(--bg);
    padding: 1rem;
  }

  svg {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    min-width: 620px;
    height: auto;
  }

  figcaption {
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
    max-width: var(--measure);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    color: var(--text-faint);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  figcaption a {
    color: var(--accent-live);
  }

  figcaption code {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    background: var(--panel);
    padding: 0.1em 0.3em;
    border-radius: 3px;
  }
</style>
